
<div class="about_text">
  <p>Welcome to Globcipe, a great app for finding recipes from around the world designed for home cooking enthusiasts.</p>
  <p>Are you looking for inspiration or want to find a recipe based on certain ingredient or from a specific cuisine or a combination of both? </p>
  <p>Globcipe offers a wide array of recipes including a detailed ingredient list and cooking instructions.</p>
  <p>A very useful feature of Globcipe is an integrated ingredient substitution list for each ingredient. </p>
  <p>So if you are missing an ingredient or can't get it in your area, don't worry the app can offer you suggestions on what to replace it with.</p>
  <p>Fell free to ask Globcipe's chatbot for any additional queries about recipes and replacements.</p>
  <p>Remember to have fun and cook away!</p>
</div>

